                                    <p class="grey_text">Have the U.S. Supreme Court's 5th Amendment Takings Decisions Changed Land Use Planning in California?</p>
                                    <p class="indent">
                                        <em>Daniel Pollak (CRB-00-004, March, 2000)</em><br />
